00:19:08.960 --> 00:19:12.220
So more important
to me is what's

00:19:12.220 --> 00:19:14.980
actually happening
in their sleep

00:19:14.980 --> 00:19:16.770
and in their own
home environment.

00:19:16.770 --> 00:19:18.730
So that's why I like to
do home sleep studies.

00:19:18.730 --> 00:19:20.900
I like to recommend
that for my patients

00:19:20.900 --> 00:19:22.975
so they can find out
what is going on.

00:19:22.975 --> 00:19:24.850
WENDY JUDSON: So that
